{"tid":2218721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍絲愛股中芯國際仆街了] 美國政府內部文件直指禁售令制裁中芯國際勢在必行","createTime":"2020-09-26T12:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T12:57:20.000Z","uid":108201,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07e043761ea559d35b710765f9ebe9471089442a","tid":2218721,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:10:27.000Z","msg":"文件指出，2020 年 4 月美國政府制裁中國華為新修訂頒布的第 744.21 節出口管制規定，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">擴大對軍事最終用途和軍事最終用戶限制，並廢除部分管制項目當前適用的民用最終用戶許可證例</span></span></strong>，擬嚴格限制管制物項再出口的許可證例外範圍。法令重點就是在防止中國、俄羅斯和委內瑞拉等國家透過民用供應鏈，或用民用供應鏈取得發展武器、軍用航空器或監視技術的美國相關科技與設備，使用到軍事和軍事最終用戶。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>現在這項規定，也準備套用到中芯國際及集團子公司。</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMMvwDp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMMvwDp.jpg&h=1127e4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點在<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">將軍事最終用途的定義擴展到「使用」、「開發」或「生產」以外任何計畫</span></strong></span>，包括運輸、安裝、保養、維修、大修、翻新軍事產品與科技等。美國商務部還提出產品和技術的出口管制條例修正案，增加數十種可用於軍事目的的新產品。這些產品出口到俄羅斯、中國和委內瑞拉時，必須向美國當局取得特別許可證。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z1MO2LQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ1MO2LQ.png&h=21a09313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國何時會頒布新制裁令，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">市場預估將是美國大選越來越近，選情越來越緊繃的時候，可能大選前的關鍵時刻就會頒布</span></strong></span>，屆時對全球半導體產業勢必掀起新一波漣漪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/09/26/sanctions-smic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F09%2F26%2Fsanctions-smic%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=0549d761\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/09/26/sanctions-smic/</a>"},{"pid":"47d7ce508b8eee746e4aa0de1816033d9c68d268","tid":2218721,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"自推一下，比藍絲親友睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4585b5a204854ec745b94504219bf99b842b752c","tid":2218721,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c273faae00aafedec0f60a8004dba91e1a4e76","tid":2218721,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713163f3bb92fcb4415a8cb42e69f920d822998b","tid":2218721,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"自推第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052908a538a06964b5b6997daeadd0d44829b480","tid":2218721,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:30:51.000Z","msg":"自推第三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a779d93ecf2460a9c0e17a3e236e00d3b073c42e","tid":2218721,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:38:41.000Z","msg":"自推第四次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9f1dd841906043ed5d5a3db9bafa29fda49701","tid":2218721,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:40:27.000Z","msg":"唉 有幾多藍友仲有中國芯？<br />\n身邊d偽藍口講愛國 走去買台獨積電<br />\n我覺得愛國真係好搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee16ff60f8553b4d4d354a06c472a47275788de","tid":2218721,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e9f1dd841906043ed5d5a3db9bafa29fda49701","tid":2218721,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:40:27.000Z","msg":"唉 有幾多藍友仲有中國芯？<br />\n身邊d偽藍口講愛國 走去買台獨積電<br />\n我覺得愛國真係好搵笨<img src=